First, we\xe2\x80\x99re updating the processors with new third generation core processors, otherwise known as Ivy Bridge. You can get speeds up to 2.7 gigahertz, and with the 15 inch up to quad-core i7 can be turbo boosted up to 3.7. The memory is also faster, upto 1600 megahertz, and the integrated graphics, which both the 13-inch and 15-inch use are also 60% faster.
