Our latest release is Lion, and Lion was the first release distributed electronically via the Mac App Store, making it easier than ever to purchase, download, and install OS X, and the results have been fantastic. We\xe2\x80\x99ve had 26 million copies shipped to-date, making it our best selling release ever.
